HydraBot: I’m HydraBot, your guide on this journey into the world of networks. [ID:D6DE25_165D89]
HydraBot: Here, you'll learn the fundamentals — how systems connect, communicate, and exchange information behind the scenes. [ID:D6DE25_9C5EDE]
