HydraBot: But here’s where things get really interesting. [ID:D6DE25_0763BE]
HydraBot: You won’t just learn theory — you’ll *build* and *experiment*. [ID:D6DE25_2EF7B2]

HydraBot: Inside HydraLearn, you’ll use the Hydra Editor — the place where the magic happens. [ID:D6DE25_B92478]
HydraBot: It’s where you’ll design, test, and truly understand how networks behave in action. [ID:D6DE25_55FA98]

HydraBot: Think of it as your personal lab. [ID:D6DE25_EA7300]
